{"tid":2137072,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人知陸龜做完手術係咪康復得好慢？","createTime":"2020-08-02T15:16:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-13T03:28:41.000Z","uid":242176,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"25e376591f892f3f424f87056aba4ab0b386828d","tid":2137072,"uid":242176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T15:16:13.000Z","msg":"我隻紅腿今年5月尾係珍禽異獸做左開龜板絕育手術，但到今時今日都係好少開口，無屎痾又少郁，淨係識訓<br />\n<br />\n其實我已經醫左6萬幾蚊，藥又開過，喉又插過，驗哂血同肝都話健康，但佢成日死死地氣咁，我已經放棄左帶佢覆診<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9GL4GzX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9GL4GzX.jpg&h=a232e7d1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"22f97493471bd0d2adbdb18cec016c877a0f3c63","tid":2137072,"uid":179867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T15:17:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d16d0adfc953cf4e620c8aaebb3e6e1231ac646","tid":2137072,"uid":242176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T15:19:57.000Z","msg":"每次去獸醫度都俾人劏咁<br />\n上次佢自己扯甩胃食喉<br />\n又要俾3千5入去做返<br />\n點知埋單7000幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做左一星期又扯甩...<br />\n決定唔再做<br />\n宜家條友訓覺都側哂頸<br />\n講真我都放棄左，由佢自己好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf7a9829fbd6741ca67ba07d73ea8045aacf6a80","tid":2137072,"uid":242176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22f97493471bd0d2adbdb18cec016c877a0f3c63","tid":2137072,"uid":179867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T15:17:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T15:20:15.000Z","msg":"都6歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9f7136bbd4e965427a9a7d98e17414df3ba1c97","tid":2137072,"uid":21920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf7a9829fbd6741ca67ba07d